trans-unit.source: Specifies the type of elements in the stack.
trans-unit.target: 指定堆栈中元素的类型。

trans-unit.source: Represents a variable size last-in-first-out (LIFO) collection of instances of the same specified type.
trans-unit.target: 表示可变大小的后进先出 (LIFO) 集合（对于相同指定类型的实例）。

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601> is implemented as an array.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601> 实现为数组。

trans-unit.source: Stacks and queues are useful when you need temporary storage for information; that is, when you might want to discard an element after retrieving its value.
trans-unit.target: 当你需要为信息; 临时存储时，堆栈和队列非常有用也就是说，当你可能想要检索其值后放弃元素。

trans-unit.source: Use <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601> if you need to access the information in the same order that it is stored in the collection.
trans-unit.target: 使用<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601>如果你需要访问集合中存储的相同顺序的信息。

trans-unit.source: Use <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601?displayProperty=nameWithType> if you need to access the information in reverse order.
trans-unit.target: 使用<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601?displayProperty=nameWithType>如果你需要按相反的顺序访问的信息。

trans-unit.source: Use the <xref:System.Collections.Concurrent.ConcurrentStack%601?displayProperty=nameWithType> and <xref:System.Collections.Concurrent.ConcurrentQueue%601?displayProperty=nameWithType> types when you need to access the collection from multiple threads concurrently.
trans-unit.target: 使用<xref:System.Collections.Concurrent.ConcurrentStack%601?displayProperty=nameWithType>和<xref:System.Collections.Concurrent.ConcurrentQueue%601?displayProperty=nameWithType>类型需要进行同时从多个线程访问集合时。

trans-unit.source: A common use for <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601?displayProperty=nameWithType> is to preserve variable states during calls to other procedures.
trans-unit.target: 一个常见用途<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601?displayProperty=nameWithType>是在调用其他过程的过程中保留变量状态。

trans-unit.source: Three main operations can be performed on a <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601?displayProperty=nameWithType> and its elements:
trans-unit.target: 可以对执行三个主要操作<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601?displayProperty=nameWithType>及其元素：

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601.Push%2A> inserts an element at the top of the <xref:System.Collections.Stack>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601.Push%2A> 在顶部插入一个元素<xref:System.Collections.Stack>。

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601.Pop%2A> removes an element from the top of the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601.Pop%2A> 从顶部移除一个元素<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601>。

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601.Peek%2A> returns an element that is at the top of the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601> but does not remove it from the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601.Peek%2A> 返回在顶部的元素<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601>但不会删除从<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601>。

trans-unit.source: The capacity of a <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601> is the number of elements the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601> can hold.
trans-unit.target: 容量<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601>是元素的数目<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601>可以保存。

trans-unit.source: As elements are added to a <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601>, the capacity is automatically increased as required by reallocating the internal array.
trans-unit.target: 如元素添加到<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601>，自动增加容量通过重新分配在内部数组所需的方式。

trans-unit.source: The capacity can be decreased by calling <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601.TrimExcess%2A>.
trans-unit.target: 可以通过调用减少容量<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601.TrimExcess%2A>。

trans-unit.source: If <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601.Count%2A> is less than the capacity of the stack, <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601.Push%2A> is an O(1) operation.
trans-unit.target: 如果<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601.Count%2A>小于的堆栈，容量<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601.Push%2A>o （1） 运算。

trans-unit.source: If the capacity needs to be increased to accommodate the new element, <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601.Push%2A> becomes an O(`n`) operation, where `n` is <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601.Count%2A>.
trans-unit.target: 如果需要增加以容纳新元素，容量<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601.Push%2A>会成为 O (`n`) 操作，其中`n`是<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601.Count%2A>。

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601.Pop%2A> is an O(1) operation.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601.Pop%2A> 是一项 o （1） 操作。

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601> accepts `null` as a valid value for reference types and allows duplicate elements.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601> 接受`null`引用为有效的值类型，并允许重复的元素。

trans-unit.source: The following code example demonstrates several methods of the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601> generic class.

trans-unit.source: The code example creates a stack of strings with default capacity and uses the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601.Push%2A> method to push five strings onto the stack.

trans-unit.target: 枚举堆栈的元素，这不会更改堆栈的状态。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601.Pop%2A> method is used to pop the first string off the stack.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601.Pop%2A>方法用于弹出堆栈的第一个字符串。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601.Peek%2A> method is used to look at the next item on the stack, and then the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601.Pop%2A> method is used to pop it off.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601.ToArray%2A> method is used to create an array and copy the stack elements to it, then the array is passed to the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601.%23ctor%2A> constructor that takes <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerable%601>, creating a copy of the stack with the order of the elements reversed.

trans-unit.source: The elements of the copy are displayed.
trans-unit.target: 显示复制的元素。

trans-unit.source: An array twice the size of the stack is created, and the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601.CopyTo%2A> method is used to copy the array elements beginning at the middle of the array.
trans-unit.target: 两次堆栈的大小将创建一个数组，和<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601.CopyTo%2A>方法用于复制数组元素在数组中间开头的位置。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601.%23ctor%2A> constructor is used again to create a copy of the stack with the order of elements reversed; thus, the three null elements are at the end.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601.%23ctor%2A>再次使用构造函数创建一份堆栈与反转的元素的顺序; 因此，三个空元素位于结尾处。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601.Contains%2A> method is used to show that the string "four" is in the first copy of the stack, after which the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601.Clear%2A> method clears the copy and the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601.Count%2A> property shows that the stack is empty.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601.Contains%2A>方法用于显示字符串"four"在堆栈上，第一个副本<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601.Clear%2A>方法清除该副本和<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601.Count%2A>属性将显示在堆栈为空。

trans-unit.source: Public static (<see langword="Shared" /> in Visual Basic) members of this type are thread safe.
trans-unit.target: 公共静态 (<see langword="Shared" />在 Visual Basic 中) 的此类型的成员都是线程安全。

trans-unit.source: Any instance members are not guaranteed to be thread safe.
trans-unit.target: 但不保证所有实例成员都是线程安全的。

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.Stack`1" /> can support multiple readers concurrently, as long as the collection is not modified.
trans-unit.target: A<see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.Stack`1" />同时，可以支持多个读取器，只要不修改该集合。

trans-unit.source: Even so, enumerating through a collection is intrinsically not a thread-safe procedure.
trans-unit.target: 即便如此，枚举整个集合本质上不是一个线程安全的过程。

trans-unit.source: To guarantee thread safety during enumeration, you can lock the collection during the entire enumeration.
trans-unit.target: 若要确保枚举过程中的线程安全性，可以在整个枚举过程中锁定集合。

trans-unit.source: To allow the collection to be accessed by multiple threads for reading and writing, you must implement your own synchronization.
trans-unit.target: 若要允许多个线程访问集合以进行读写操作，则必须实现自己的同步。

trans-unit.source: Enumerators can be used to read the data in the collection, but they cannot be used to modify the underlying collection.

trans-unit.source: Initially, the enumerator is positioned before the first element in the collection.
trans-unit.target: 最初，枚举数定位在集合中第一个元素的前面。

trans-unit.source: At this position, <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601.Enumerator.Current%2A> is undefined.
trans-unit.target: 在此位置上，未定义 <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601.Enumerator.Current%2A>。

trans-unit.source: Therefore, you must call <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A> to advance the enumerator to the first element of the collection before reading the value of <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601.Enumerator.Current%2A>.
trans-unit.target: 因此，在读取 <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A> 的值之前，必须调用 <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601.Enumerator.Current%2A> 将枚举器向前移动到集合的第一个元素。

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601.Enumerator.Current%2A> returns the same object until <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A> is called.
trans-unit.target: 在调用 <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601.Enumerator.Current%2A> 之前，<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A> 返回相同的对象。

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A> sets <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601.Enumerator.Current%2A> to the next element.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A> 将 <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601.Enumerator.Current%2A> 设置为下一个元素。

trans-unit.source: If <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A> passes the end of the collection, the enumerator is positioned after the last element in the collection and <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A> returns `false`.
trans-unit.target: 如果<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A>越过的末尾的集合，枚举数定位在集合中的最后一个元素的后面和<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A>返回`false`。

trans-unit.source: When the enumerator is at this position, subsequent calls to <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A> also return `false`.
trans-unit.target: 当枚举器位于此位置上，后续调用<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A>还返回`false`。

trans-unit.source: If the last call to <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A> returned `false`, <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601.Enumerator.Current%2A> is undefined.
trans-unit.target: 如果最后一次调用到<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A>返回`false`，<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601.Enumerator.Current%2A>是不确定的。

trans-unit.source: You cannot set <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601.Enumerator.Current%2A> to the first element of the collection again; you must create a new enumerator instance instead.
trans-unit.target: 无法再次将 <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601.Enumerator.Current%2A> 设置为集合的第一个元素；必须改为创建新的枚举器实例。

trans-unit.source: An enumerator remains valid as long as the collection remains unchanged.
trans-unit.target: 只要集合保持不变，枚举数就保持有效。

trans-unit.source: If changes are made to the collection, such as adding, modifying, or deleting elements, the enumerator is irrecoverably invalidated and its behavior is undefined.
trans-unit.target: 如果对集合进行更改（如添加、修改或删除元素），则枚举数将失效且不可恢复，而且其行为是不确定的。

trans-unit.source: The enumerator does not have exclusive access to the collection; therefore, enumerating through a collection is intrinsically not a thread-safe procedure.
trans-unit.target: 枚举数没有对集合的独占访问权；因此，从头到尾对一个集合进行枚举在本质上不是一个线程安全的过程。

trans-unit.source: To guarantee thread safety during enumeration, you can lock the collection during the entire enumeration.
trans-unit.target: 若要确保枚举过程中的线程安全性，可以在整个枚举过程中锁定集合。

trans-unit.source: To allow the collection to be accessed by multiple threads for reading and writing, you must implement your own synchronization.
trans-unit.target: 若要允许多个线程访问集合以进行读写操作，则必须实现自己的同步。

trans-unit.target: 集合中的默认实现<xref:System.Collections.Generic?displayProperty=nameWithType>不同步。

trans-unit.source: The following code example demonstrates several methods of the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601> generic class, including the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601.ToArray%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: 下面的代码示例演示的若干方法<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601>泛型类，包括<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601.ToArray%2A>方法。

trans-unit.source: The code example creates a stack of strings with default capacity and uses the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601.Push%2A> method to push five strings onto the stack.
trans-unit.target: 此代码示例的字符串堆栈创建具有默认容量并使用<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601.Push%2A>方法推送到堆栈的五个字符串。

trans-unit.source: The elements of the stack are enumerated, which does not change the state of the stack.
trans-unit.target: 枚举堆栈的元素，这不会更改堆栈的状态。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601.Pop%2A> method is used to pop the first string off the stack.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601.Pop%2A>方法用于弹出堆栈的第一个字符串。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601.Peek%2A> method is used to look at the next item on the stack, and then the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601.Pop%2A> method is used to pop it off.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601.Peek%2A>方法用于在堆栈中，查找在下一项，然后<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601.Pop%2A>方法用于其弹出。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601.ToArray%2A> method is used to create an array and copy the stack elements to it, then the array is passed to the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601.%23ctor%2A> constructor that takes <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerable%601>, creating a copy of the stack with the order of the elements reversed.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601.ToArray%2A>方法用于创建数组并将堆栈元素复制到它，然后，数组传递给<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601.%23ctor%2A>构造函数采用<xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerable%601>，创建一份堆栈与元素的顺序反转。

trans-unit.source: The elements of the copy are displayed.
trans-unit.target: 显示复制的元素。

trans-unit.source: An array twice the size of the stack is created, and the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601.CopyTo%2A> method is used to copy the array elements beginning at the middle of the array.
trans-unit.target: 两次堆栈的大小将创建一个数组，和<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601.CopyTo%2A>方法用于复制数组元素在数组中间开头的位置。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601.%23ctor%2A> constructor is used again to create a copy of the stack with the order of elements reversed; thus, the three null elements are at the end.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601.%23ctor%2A>再次使用构造函数创建一份堆栈与反转的元素的顺序; 因此，三个空元素位于结尾处。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601.Contains%2A> method is used to show that the string "four" is in the first copy of the stack, after which the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601.Clear%2A> method clears the copy and the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601.Count%2A> property shows that the stack is empty.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601.Contains%2A>方法用于显示字符串"four"在堆栈上，第一个副本<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601.Clear%2A>方法清除该副本和<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601.Count%2A>属性将显示在堆栈为空。

trans-unit.source: Sets the capacity to the actual number of elements in the <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.Stack`1" />, if that number is less than 90 percent of current capacity.
trans-unit.target: 如果元素数小于当前容量的 90%，将容量设置为 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.Stack`1" /> 中的实际元素数。

trans-unit.source: This method can be used to minimize a collection's memory overhead if no new elements will be added to the collection.
trans-unit.target: 此方法可以用于降低集合的内存开销，如果没有新的元素将添加到集合。

trans-unit.source: The cost of reallocating and copying a large <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601> can be considerable, however, so the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601.TrimExcess%2A> method does nothing if the list is at more than 90 percent of capacity.
trans-unit.target: 重新分配和复制较大的成本<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601>但是，可能很大，因此<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601.TrimExcess%2A>方法不执行任何操作如果列表为在多个容量的 90%。

trans-unit.source: This avoids incurring a large reallocation cost for a relatively small gain.
trans-unit.target: 这样可以避免产生的相对较小有所提高大型重新分配费用。

trans-unit.source: This method is an O(`n`) operation, where `n` is <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601.Count%2A>.
trans-unit.target: 此方法为 O (`n`) 操作，其中`n`是<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601.Count%2A>。

trans-unit.source: To reset a <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601> to its initial state, call the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601.Clear%2A> method before calling <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601.TrimExcess%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: 若要重置<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601>为其初始状态，请在调用<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601.Clear%2A>方法之前调用<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601.TrimExcess%2A>方法。

trans-unit.source: Trimming an empty <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601> sets the capacity of the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601> to the default capacity.
trans-unit.target: 截去空<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601>的容量设置<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601>到默认的容量。
